para_trans: Main article: "2045 Vendors on Goods and Services"

Industries, Energy, Labour and Mining Department,
Demand No. K-1, Main Account Heading 2045 Vendor Goods and Services for this fiscal year 2024-25
The revised provision under Other Taxes and Duties (Compulsory) (Deductible) on these is Rs. 95,79,83, 000 / -

Requests for funds received from the Office of the Chief Electrical Inspector
As it did not, the revised provision of Rs. 87.86645 was noted. Out of the revised provision of Rs. 86.90337, the remaining provision has been returned by disbursement of the target fund.
